org.routamc.positioning ChangeLog
---------------------------------

Legend:
- All items marked with "!" represent a major API-Change that is
  not guaranteed to be backwards compatible to previous versions
  which might even break existing functionality.
- All items marked with "+" represent completely new features.

2007-09-13 bergie
  + Added XEP-0080 compatible civic location attributes for the location object
  + Added new geocoding service with local city database, Yahoo! and GeoNames as backends

2007-08-20 bergie
  + Added country information to the database

2007-07-16 bergie
  + Bundled the mapstraction map display library
  + Created a new org_routamc_positioning_map wrapper for map display

2007-04-11 bergie
  + Initial, quick-and-dirty handling of timezoneless Plazes trace information

2007-01-10 bergie
  + Switched Plazes implementation to the Plazes API 1.0

2006-11-30 bergie
  ! Switched to utilize Midgard 1.8 metadata

2006-10-30 bergie
  + Made several fixes for manual object positioning
  + Added support for GeoRSS subscriptions (both W3C and GeoRSS Simple formats)

2006-10-22 bergie
  + Added support for manually specified person and time for objects
